<recipe lang="en-uk" xmlns:lxslt="http://xml.apache.org/xslt">
<title><![CDATA[Impanata di spinaci / Spinach pasty]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[There are many variations. Not all the options here go together - either raisins, or sausage, or mozzarella.]]></description>
<source/>
<img></img>
<cuisine>
<style>Italian</style>
<region>Sicilian</region>
<approach/>
</cuisine>
<tags>
<tag/>
</tags>
<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[dissolve fresh yeast in warm water for 5m. Add flour bit by bit and knead for 10m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[rest in greased bowl, covered in kitchen towel until doubled in size, about 2h]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sauté garlic in olive oil hot until just golden, about 1m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sauté spinach until just wilted, about 3m. Drain, squeeze well keeping the water, and chop corasely]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[soak raisins, if using, in spinach water for 10m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[drain and add to chopped spinach]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add chili powder if using, black olives, mozzarella if using]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[If using sausage, sauté onion in olive oil med for 4m, add sausage until seared, about 2m. then set aside.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Mix all the fillings together in a bowl]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Roll out dough as thin as possible, smear oil over it, lay the stuffing over it. Start rolling, smearing more oil between layers of dough]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Bake until ready 190° for 35m]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
